# Vulnerabilities knowingly accepted, with justification and review owner.
# Format: one CVE ID per line; lines starting with '#' are comments.

# ── pillow 12.x bumps ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Moving from pillow 11.x to 12.x is a major version bump that needs
# coordinated testing with TF, scikit-image and the academic pipeline.
# Tracked separately; rotate the date and revisit once the upgrade lands.
# Reviewed: 2026-05-21 — Louis
CVE-2026-25990
